cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR

The paper proposes a deep learning framework for crowd flow prediction, which involves spatio-temporal modeling and transfer learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which covers deep learning and transfer learning. The paper also leverages social network check-ins to link regions in different cities, which involves social network analysis and information retrieval, suggesting cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as likely categories. The paper also deals with image data (maps) and proposes a neural network structure, which suggests cs.CV (Computer Vision) as a possible category. Finally, the paper involves prediction and forecasting, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another possible category.
